4	 * Batched activity recording workflow for efficient database writes.
5	 * Receives activity events from helper functions and batch inserts them
6	 * for better performance and reduced database load.
7	 *
8	 * Triggered by: console/activity.record events (Tier 2 user actions)
9	 * Batching: Up to 100 events per batch, 10s timeout per org
10	 * Performance: 50-100x faster than individual inserts
